==-. ABS Backup System .-==

ABS is free software, released under the GNU GPL3 or (at your option) any
later version; see the file LICENSE for the details.

1. QUICK START

  1. Copy abs to /usr/local/sbin/abs
  2. Edit and copy abs.conf to /usr/local/etc/abs/abs.conf
  3. Edit and copy exclude.conf to /usr/local/etc/abs/exclude.conf
  4. Copy abs.cron to /etc/cron.d/abs

